        "Boma"
      ],
      "text": "Boma was Avatar Yangchen's chaperone on her journey to a city that was being plagued by the spirit of General Old Iron."
    },
    {
      "body": "When Yangchen was summoned toward a city on the shoreline of the ${link_0} a week after she mastered all ${link_1}, Boma accompanied her there, despite Yangchen's protests that she would be fine on her own. He had refuted those claims, stating that he had promised the ${link_2} nuns that he would look after her until she was ready to be on her own and that it was never a good idea to break a promise to a nun. During the Avatar's audience with the king, Boma was present as well, taking care of Yangchen's two ${link_3}, ${link_4}, whom he comforted after they were scared by the local fortunetellers.",
