      "text": "Believing the prophecy that something bad was to befall the city from the sea, Boma accompanied Yangchen on her stakeout on a cliff overlooking the water. When General Old Iron appeared and knocked Yangchen down, he helped her up and urged her to stop the rampaging spirit while he evacuated all the citizens to a nearby clearing."
    },
    {
      "body": "Boma stood alongside Yangchen as she finished a memorial to Lady ${link_0}, fulfilling her deal with Old Iron to keep the townspeople safe.",
